The platform is designed for three primary user groups:
Job Seekers
Individuals searching for employment opportunities.
Require advanced job search, resume uploads, and application tracking.
Benefit from AI-powered job recommendations based on their qualifications.
Employers & Recruiters
Companies posting vacancies and managing applicants through dashboards.
Need features like resume screening, candidate communication, and analytics tools.
Administrators
Oversee platform operations, ensuring data security, compliance, and fraud prevention.
